                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-1-off1 t18220417-1-cd2"></join>, one handkerchief, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18220417-1-victim54" type="victimName">
                        Thomas 
                        Rees
